---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Speaking"
  description="Book Jason Ehlinger for keynotes and workshops on leadership, personal finance, and building a life of purpose."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="section-label">Speaking & Events</span>
    <h1>A Speaker Who's<br/>Actually Done It.</h1>
    <p>No corporate buzzwords. No generic advice. Real stories, proven frameworks, and audiences that leave ready to act.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:780px;">
      <span class="section-label">Why Hire Jason</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:1.8rem; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Every Talk Is Built on Experience, Not Theory</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray); margin-bottom:1.25rem; font-size:1.05rem;">As CEO of Taika Translations, a U.S. Air Force veteran, husband, and father of 8, Jason brings a perspective that's both grounded and expansive. He's built a 7-figure business from zero, led teams through every stage of growth, saved $100k on a military salary, and navigated the hardest conversations — at work and at home.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--gray);">He also hosts weekly live masterclasses and has published 777+ videos on leadership and finance — so he knows how to communicate complex ideas in ways that land with real people.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOPICS -->
  <section class="section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Speaking Topics</span>
        <h2>What Jason Speaks On</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="card-grid">

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">⚙️</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">The Leadership Operating System</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Stop managing tasks. Start inspiring people. Jason delivers the full framework from his 13-part "Forge" masterclass — covering accountability structures, decision-making, vision creation, vulnerability-based trust, and escaping the Operator's Trap.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Organizations, leadership teams, entrepreneurs</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🧱</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">How to Build a Great Team</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Based on Patrick Lencioni's framework and Jason's own experience scaling Taika Translations — covering company culture, clarifying purpose, building trust, and eliminating the wrong priorities so your team can focus on what actually moves the needle.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Executive teams, business owners, HR leaders</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">💰</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Building Wealth From Zero</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">No investors, no trust fund — just a card table and a plan. Jason shares the money frameworks behind building a 7-figure business and his family's personal wealth journey, including zero-based budgeting, the mindset shifts that compound over time, and why working hard but staying broke is a system problem, not an income problem.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Young professionals, families, community groups</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">⚔️</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">From Uniform to Entrepreneur</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">The military gives you discipline and structure — but transitioning to entrepreneurship requires a completely different operating system. Jason shares what no one tells veterans about civilian leadership, and how to build on military experience without getting trapped by it.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Veterans, transition programs, VOB events</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🏠</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Money, Marriage & Mission</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Money red flags, green flags, and the conversations that determine whether couples win or lose financially. With 8 kids and a 7-figure business, Jason and his wife have had every version of this conversation. He shares what works — and what destroys financial partnerships before they start.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Couples, faith communities, family-focused organizations</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🎯</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Purpose, Discipline & the Unbreakable Mindset</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Why your reason for working determines everything. Why security is an illusion — and why that's actually freeing. How to recover after total failure. How your toughest season becomes your greatest blessing. A faith-informed, experience-backed talk on building a life with clarity, grit, and intention.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Faith communities, men's groups, leadership conferences</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">📈</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Goal Setting: The Truth Nobody Tells You</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">What really happens when you miss the deadline. How to set goals that actually matter, build systems to hit them, and recalibrate without losing momentum. Practical, honest, and built from real experience — not a motivational poster.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Corporate teams, annual kickoffs, entrepreneurship events</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <div style="color:var(--gold); font-size:1.75rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">🔥</div>
          <h3 style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Mastering Tough Conversations as a Leader</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.95rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">The 5 essential skills every leader needs to handle difficult conversations without destroying trust or avoiding conflict. Based on real scenarios from building and leading a growing company — not theoretical frameworks from a textbook.</p>
          <p style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#999;">Best for: Managers, team leads, mid-level leaders</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FORMATS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:800px;">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Formats</span>
        <h2>How Jason Speaks</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem;">
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🎤</div>
          <h3 style="font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Keynote</h3>
          <p style="color:var(--gray); font-size:0.9rem;">45–75 minutes. High-energy, story-driven, actionable. Perfect for conferences and annual events.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center; padding:2rem; background:var(--light-gray); border-radius:4px;">
          <div style="font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:0.75rem;">🛠</div>
          <h3 style="font-